nuary%2525202023.">分析报告</a>，称该应用程序的参与度已大幅下降，称它仍有 2000 万日活跃用户。该公司承认，虽然幕后一直很忙，但最近并没有发布很多新功能，所以“人们一直在猜测我们在做什么以及事情的进展情况，但并不总是准确的。</p><p>在过去的几个月里，尽管它已经启动了<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://newsroom.spotify.com/2023-04-19/our-new-integration-allows-you-to-share-music-and-podcasts-on-bereal-heres-how/">与 Spotify 的集成，</a>可以显示您在发布时正在收听的内容，以及<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bereal-says-it-has-more-than-20-million-daily-active-users-172721921.html">Bonus BeReal</a>功能，如果您按时发布，则可以发布多个 BeReal。与其他社交媒体应用程序一样，RealChat 功能看起来像是一种增加在该应用程序上花费的时间并允许朋友私下评论帖子的方法。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/bereal-is-testing-a-direct-messaging-feature-called-realchat-132602404.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/bereal-is-testing-a-direct-messaging-feature-called-realchat-132602404.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> aaab2b86-33a6-4e97-bd61-41292531bdca</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 01 Jun 2023 13:26:02 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685625963</ingested><modified> 2023-06-01T13:26:07+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mobile Apps]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="2671" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/2c684da0-0079-11ee-ab67-36ea2d640d5f" width="4015"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_